                  , in the parish of <placeName id="t17840707-82-crimeloc412">St. Clement Danes</placeName>
                     <interp inst="t17840707-82-crimeloc412" type="placeName" value="St. Clement Danes"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t17840707-82-crimeloc412" type="type" value="crimeLocation"></interp>
                     <join result="offencePlace" targOrder="Y" targets="t17840707-82-off411 t17840707-82-crimeloc412"></join> in the county of Middlesex, on the 1st of July, and feloniously stealing therein, one linen gown, value 10 s. and one linen shift, value 12 d. the property of 
                     
                        <persName id="t17840707-82-victim816" type="victimName">
                           Elizabeth 
                           Small
                        <interp inst="t17840707-82-victim816" type="surname" value="Small"></interp>
